      "comment": "ZIPPING LAMBERT (7) proved too good last time out claiming his maiden success at this track over 320m (18.54). Can measure up again. SPRING ORCHID (2) flew the lids and led throughout to get off the mark with her maiden win, then finished a 6 length third last start at this track over 320m (19.00). Has placed one times at this track. Can measure up this time. BLUE OPAL (1) scored an on-pace win two back then gave a start and could manage only 3rd at Bulli (19.84) last time. Comes through a solid form race last start. Expected to be in this for a long way. SPRING ARROW (8) should be thereabouts after filling a top-three at this track and distance most recently.",
